*七星中會議長（2020～2021）<ref>{{cite web |author1=黃春生 |title=我的蒙召與見證 |url=http://www.laijohn.com/archives/pc/Ng/Ng,Cseng/testimony/call.htm |website=賴永祥資料庫 |accessdate=2020-08-18 |archive-date=2020-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928145943/http://laijohn.com/archives/pc/Ng/Ng,Cseng/testimony/call.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

